comments: LaVine (CHI) is turning slightly as he braces for the contact with Curry (GSW) during the pick, which he absorbs.
Looney (GSW) briefly has his hand on Carter Jr.'s (CHI) right hip and momentarily grasps Carter Jr.'s jersey before quickly releasing.
Carter Jr. (CHI) re-establishes himself in Oubre Jr.'s (GSW) path after initial contact takes place, and the proceeding contact is marginal.
Porter Jr. (CHI) and Curry (GSW) come together during rebounding and marginal contact occurs to Curry's backside as they each attempt to retrieve the ball.
Porter Jr. (CHI) swipes and, after making initial contact with the ball, some marginal contact occurs with Wiggins' (GSW) right forearm.
LaVine (CHI) maintains legal guarding position as body contact occurs with Wiggins (GSW) at the end of the drive.
White (CHI) and Wiggins (GSW) make incidental contact with one another as they each attempt to gain control of the rebound.
Carter Jr. (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Wiggins' (GSW) path and does not deliver the contact.
Lee (GSW) cleanly blocks LaVine's (CHI) driving shot attempt.

Looney (GSW) maintains legal guarding position as body contact occurs with LaVine (CHI) after his gather. Looney then brings his arm down after the release and incidental contact occurs with LaVine's right wrist after his shot is blocked by Lee (GSW).
Oubre Jr. (GSW) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Wiggins (GSW) briefly grasps and then quickly releases Carter Jr.'s (CHI) right arm during rebounding.
Carter Jr. (CHI) jumps from point A to point B and initiates body contact with Curry (GSW) during the driving shot attempt.
After the hand-off, Satoransky (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Oubre Jr.'s (GSW) path and does not deliver the contact.
Oubre Jr. (GSW) moves into LaVine (CHI) and makes body contact that affects his SQBR.
Looney (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in Satoransky's (CHI) path and does not deliver the contact.
Carter Jr.'s (CHI) arms are not in a perfectly vertical position but the contact with Wiggins (GSW) occurs to the body and he absorbs the contact.
Carter Jr. (CHI) makes incidental contact with Wiggins' (GSW) right arm after the release of his put-back attempt.
Carter Jr. (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Oubre Jr.'s (GSW) path and does not deliver the contact.
Oubre Jr. (GSW) extends his left arm forward and some marginal contact occurs with LaVine's (CHI) front as LaVine dribbles near half-court.
LaVine (CHI) goes to, not through, Toscano-Anderson's (GSW) space after coming together, and LaVine's arm naturally releases forward as he shifts his momentum backward.
Toscano-Anderson (GSW) is moving alongside LaVine's (CHI) path and he absorbs the body contact made with LaVine after they come together.
Lee (GSW) fails to inbound the ball within five seconds.
Looney (GSW) continues to re-establish himself in White's (CHI) path after initial contact and he delivers contact to White that affects his ability to defend.
